title: For Sale:  M 48 Mauser
postcontent: I have an M 48 Mauser for sale that is new, unfired. I woudl imagine it was test fired after manufacture but I received it in its original cosmoline wrapped paper from 1956. After a thorough cleaning, this rifle is in new condition and pristine. I am in the process of taking photos. The M 48 has three changes from the German K 98. Its action and bolt were made shorter to reduce cycle time in cocking and extracting rounds. Secondly the butt plate was redesigned to cup the entier end of the stock replacing the plate. Lastly the follower was made to allow the bolt to ride forward eliminating the need to depress it. Their is also a smll change on the top of the stock with one more handguard than the K 98. Other than that, it is a Mauser built on german technology  after WWIIIf your looking for a pristine Mauser that was a WWII weapon that was never issued never fired, and is new, this is it.This rifle has all its original parts in new condition. This rifle is not for every one but someone who wants and can afford a one of a kind new, unfired mauser manufactured circa 1956Photos are in processFeel free to contact me with any questions.
